Og8Q">Thất tịch - 七夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%B4ng-Tuy%E1%BB%81n-huy%E1%BB%87n-th%E1%BB%B1-%E1%BB%91c-b%C3%ADch-h%E1%BA%ADu-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-thi%E1%BA%BFu-b%E1%BA%A3o-ho%E1%BA%A1-h%E1%BA%A1c/poem-wQIQaYRNmxgR3IKYtZBebA">Thông Tuyền huyện thự ốc bích hậu Tiết thiếu bảo hoạ hạc - 通泉縣署屋壁後薛少保畫鶴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%C3%ADch-hoa-t%E1%BB%A9-lu%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BB%99-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-T%C3%A0ng-Xu%C3%A2n-vi%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n-v%E1%BA%ADn-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-bUAdypQNXUXEipKq--T1lg">Tích hoa tứ luật bộ Tương Châu Tàng Xuân viên chủ nhân vận kỳ 3 - 惜花四律步湘州藏春園主人韻其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-zD7mrwO-43MIHObHTaGOMw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh tự - 送尚書柴莊卿序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/author-1_5YGABQESnAmYdOvhbEZQ">Lý Khiêm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
